dct_title_s: Rand McNally standard map of Nevada
dct_alternative_sm: Nevada Rand McNally indexed pocket map. Tourists's and shippers' guide
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Pocket map showing railroads and township and range grid.
"Main highways, railroads, electric lines, counties, cities, towns, villages, post offices, lakes, rivers, etc."
Includes index to principal cities and lists their populations.

Rand McNally black and white mileage map California and Nevada with inset maps of the San Francisco and Los Angeles areas, and index to counties, lakes, mountains, rivers, towns, etc. for Nevada on the verso.
Originally published as pages 330-331 of Rand McNally's commercial atlas of America.
